snippet: Shaylee Chuckulnaskit, who was shot in the head last week when a classmate fired on five classmates in Marysville, Wash., died at a hospital in Everett.
abstract: Shaylee Chuckulnaskit, 14-year-old girl shot and critically wounded when classmate Jaylen Ray Fryberg opened fire at Marysville-Pilchuck High School in Washington State, dies.
lead_paragraph: Shaylee Chuckulnaskit, who was shot in the head last week when a classmate fired on five classmates in Marysville, Wash., died at a hospital in Everett.

headline.main: Girl, 14, Dies of Wounds in Washington School Shooting
headline.print_headline: Girl Shot at Washington School Dies
